SIZE=(17,67), ORIENT=(02,07)
WINDOW BOX
EASEL ON


                  Validation Option - Help

    Used to determine how to handle relationships that have
    failed validation requirements.  Valid entries are:

      D  Remove the relationship immediately.
      N  Set relationship to a "Validation Failed" status if
         the relationship failed the validation requirements.
      Y  Set relationship to a "Validation Failed" status and
         calculate the VF Expiration Date based on the validation
         failure options on MICM Record 7100 (Institution
         Parameters) and MICM Record 7101 (Model Definition).
                                                                _
    F12=Cancel                                            M00055S

EASEL OFF
LABEL=(LABEL,IMPORTANT)
FIELD=PFKEY,    PIC='X(01)', ATTR=(DISPLAY,HIDDEN)
LABEL=(LABEL,IMPORTANT)
